ZH: 我小时候喜欢玩弹珠。
EN: I used to love playing marbles when I was a child.

ZH: 弟弟在学校里买了一颗漂亮的弹珠。
EN: My younger brother bought a beautiful marble at school.

ZH: 这颗弹珠是我和朋友一起玩游戏赢来的。
EN: This marble was won by me and my friends while playing games.

ZH: 他用一颗白色的弹珠撞击其他弹珠。
EN: He used a white marble to hit the other marbles.

ZH: 我在游戏中赢得了一袋弹珠作为奖励。
EN: I won a bag of marbles as a prize in the game.

ZH: 弟弟把他的弹珠都放在一个小袋子里。
EN: My younger brother keeps all his marbles in a small bag.

ZH: 这个花纹漂亮的弹珠是我妹妹送给我的礼物。
EN: This beautifully patterned marble was a gift from my sister.

ZH: 弹珠是一个流行的传统玩具。
EN: Marbles are a popular traditional toy.

ZH: 我们在操场上举办了一场弹珠比赛。
EN: We organized a marble competition on the playground.

ZH: 你知道如何玩弹珠吗？
EN: Do you know how to play marbles?

