EN: Marbles is a game that tests patience and concentration.

ZH: 我教会了我的小姐妹如何玩弹珠。
EN: I taught my little sister how to play marbles.

ZH: 我把这些弹珠都收集起来放在一个盒子里。
EN: I collected all these marbles and put them in a box.

